show.description: After being betrayed and cast out, Siya returns with a secret child and a storm of unresolved truths — igniting an explosive clash with her powerful ex, Ranbir. As supernatural legacies and dark pasts unfold, love, revenge, and power collide in a world where no one is truly human.
